payload.message:
Please apply this compaction config upgrade. Run this exact config.patch via your gateway tool:

{"agents":{"defaults":{"compaction":{"mode":"safeguard","memoryFlush":{"enabled":true},"qualityGuard":{"enabled":true,"maxRetries":1},"postCompactionSections":["Every Session","Safety"],"recentTurnsPreserve":5}}}}

This enables: memory flush before compaction, quality guard with 1 retry, post-compaction section re-injection, and 5 recent turns preserved. Approved by Guillermo.
